1. *Uređaj* je bio napravljen da pomogne ljudima u njihovim svakodnevnim aktivnostima. (The device was made to help people in their everyday activities.)

2. *Uređaj* je bio napravljen od najboljih materijala. (The device was made of the best materials.)

3. Oni su koristili najmodernije *uređaje* da bi dobili željeni rezultat. (They used the most modern devices to get the desired result.)

4. *Uređaj* je bio dizajniran da bude jednostavan za korišćenje. (The device was designed to be easy to use.)

5. *Uređaj* je bio testiran pre nego što je pušten u prodaju. (The device was tested before it was released for sale.)